member.summary:
Updates the register names and fuse sizes for the active namespace.
Ensures that HCS and FDS register names and their corresponding sizes are tracked per namespace.


This method is called during initialization to set up the mapping between register names and fuse sizes
for each unique namespace encountered in the BISR configuration.



var registerNames = new Dictionary<string, HeapRegister> { ... };
UpdateRegisterNameAndFuseSize(registerNames);
